# Recommendations

## High Priority

- Validate empty usernames.
- Hash passwords before storage.
- Never store credentials in plain text.

---

## Medium Priority

- Separate validation logic into helper functions.
- Improve email validation.
- Return descriptive errors instead of `None`.

---

## Low Priority

- Add type hints.
- Add documentation.
- Write automated unit tests.
- Improve scalability by replacing the global list with persistent storage.

